\c 108
\s Umkhuleko wokucela ukusizwa lokunqoba
\d Ingoma, isihlabelelo sikaDavida
\p
\v 1 Inhliziyo yami iqinile, Nkulunkulu. Ngizahlabelela ngitshotshe, ngitsho udumo lwami\x + 108.5, Hlab. 57.7-11.\x*!
\p
\v 2 Vukani gubhu lwezintambo lechacho! Ngizavusa ukusa.
\v 3 Ngizakudumisa, N\nd kosi\nd*, phakathi kwabantu, ngihlabele indumiso kuwe phakathi kwezizwe.
\v 4 Ngoba umusa wakho mkhulu phezu kwamazulu\x + Hlab. 113.4. Jer. 51.9.\x*, leqiniso lakho lifika emayezini\x + Hlab. 68.34.\x*.
\v 5 Phakama, Nkulunkulu, ngaphezu kwamazulu, lobukhosi bakho phezu komhlaba wonke\x + Hlab. 113.4. Jer. 51.9.\x*.
\v 6 Ukuze abathandekayo bakho bakhululwe; sindisa \add nge\add*sandla sakho sokunene, ungiphendule\x + Hlab. 60.5-12.\x*.
\p
\v 7 UNkulunkulu ukhulumile ebungcweleni bakhe. Ngizathaba, ngiyabe iShekema, ngilinganise isihotsha seSukothi.
\v 8 Ngeyami iGileyadi, ngowami uManase, loEfrayimi ungamandla ekhanda lami, uJuda ungumnikumthetho wami.
\v 9 UMowabi ungumganu wami wokugezela; phezu kukaEdoma ngizaphosela inyathela lami; mayelana lami, wena Filisti\x + 2 Sam. 8.1.\x*, memeza ngokunqoba.
\p
\v 10 Ngubani ozangisa emzini oqinileyo? Ngubani ozangiholela eEdoma\x + Hlab. 65.13. Hlab. 60.8.\x*\x + Josh. 19.29.\x*?
\v 11 Kawusilahlanga yini, Nkulunkulu; kawuphumanga, Nkulunkulu, lamabutho ethu\x + Hlab. 44.9. 60.10.\x*?
\v 12 Siphe usizo ekuhlupheni, ngoba luyize uncedo lomuntu.
\v 13 KuNkulunkulu sizakwenza ngobuqhawe, ngoba yena uzanyathelela phansi izitha zethu.
